@model Prediction

<div style="text-align: center; list-style-position: inside; ">
    
    <h1 >Severity:@Model.PredictedValue</h1>
    <h5 >Severity Scale</h5>

    <ol>
        <li>No injury</li>
        <li>Possible injury</li>
        <li>Suspected minor injury</li>
        <li>Suspected serious injury</li>
        <li>Fatal</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        This predictor is able to predict the severity of a crash based on many different details and scenarios. It is can be used to see what kind of danger someone is in when driving under those conditions. By educating and teaching we will be able to create safer situations for everyone around us. 
    </p>
</div>

